        "subject": "LU-12187 lod: trivial EC cstripe/dstripe support",
        "message": "LU-12187 lod: trivial EC cstripe/dstripe support\n\nCorrectly store cstripe and dstripe counts in EC, but\ndon't use them for anything yet.  They can be handled\nvia the layout API, but not yet via setstripe/getstripe.\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I9e19417f417ba10ad871f19d44d2559ca82b254b\n"
